snippet.title: Pretty Pet Salon
snippet.description:
Available on Google Play: http://goo.gl/gZrYt

This cute & casual game is sure to keep you entertained with hours of addictive pet-grooming fun!

- Get ready to run your very own Pet Salon!
- Serve customers, earn money, and make your shop bigger and better!
- Grow your staff, and hire new employees bursting with personality and cuteness!
- Compete with your friends all over the world for the best and most successful Pet Salon out there!
- Exciting new achievements for you to collect!
- Just be sure to keep an eye out for two special celebrity guest customers... they'll give your Pet Salon a real surprise!

Check out the official Pretty Pet Salon Facebook page: http://facebook.com/PrettyPetSalon
